<Base title="About — Morocco Art Guide">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="page-header" style="text-align: left;">
      <span class="micro-label">About</span>
      <h1>About This Guide</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p>Morocco Art Guide is a comprehensive reference to Moroccan visual art — the artists, movements, institutions, and cities that make up one of Africa's most dynamic art scenes.</p>

      <p>The guide documents painters, sculptors, photographers, and multimedia artists from the founding of the Casablanca School in the 1960s to the contemporary galleries reshaping Marrakech and Casablanca today. It maps museums, galleries, artist residencies, and cultural centres across the country.</p>

      <p>This is not a marketplace. We don't sell art. We document it — who made it, why it matters, and where you can see it.</p>

      <h2>A Slow Morocco Project</h2>

      <p>Morocco Art Guide is a project of <a href="https://www.slowmorocco.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Slow Morocco</a>, an independent cultural intelligence platform documenting Morocco through travel, craft, food, architecture, and the visual arts.</p>

      <p>For questions, corrections, or contributions: <a href="mailto:hello@slowmorocco.com">hello@slowmorocco.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

